column5: Who else watches them....Skynard shock my house down tonight......
I get an email from them , usually Friday with the Sunday Concert Schedule, will watch if there is something that suits my taste in music. Sign up online for the email, no spam from them either.
I watch alot of them.  The sound is phenomenal on most, and the picture is nice too.  It usually feels about as close to being there as you can get
